---
title: Carb Smart Almond Turkey with Green Veggies and Lemony Mayo
description: This is not your nonna's fried cutlet! Inspired by the restaurant classic, tender turkey is topped with a wholesome crust, and we've swapped breadcrumbs out for almonds to keep those carbs low. A tumble of garlicky green veggies is always a good idea.

Carb Smart (50 g carbohydrates or less) is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.
